395
00:23:59,766 --> 00:24:02,501
Oh, yes. Right you are, Mr. Brewster.

396
00:24:02,601 --> 00:24:06,062
I'd like to get $3 million in cash
now and take it with me.

397
00:24:06,729 --> 00:24:09,506
