00:25:21,775 --> 00:25:22,776
For what?

427
00:25:23,651 --> 00:25:24,676
Strike!

428
00:25:24,776 --> 00:25:27,344
Watch the goddamn ball, Johnson!

429
00:25:27,444 --> 00:25:31,113
You're not a farmer! You don't have
